trans-unit.source: The CmsRecipientEnumerator class provides enumeration functionality for the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

The Current property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the current recipient in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

The MoveNext method advances the enumeration to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the enumeration successfully moved to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the enumeration moved past the last item in the enumeration.

The Reset method resets the enumeration to the first <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

The IEnumerator.Current property retrieves the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient"></xref> object that represents the current recipient in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection"></xref> collection.
